        <p style="font-family:Mulish;font-weight:600;font-size:24px;line-height:1.5;color:#fff;margin:0 0 36px;">You don&rsquo;t need to be at breaking point.<br />You don&rsquo;t need to have it all together.<br />You&rsquo;re allowed support too.</p>
